<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>
    <style>
      .download-section {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdfa 0%, #dbeafe 50%, #fef2f2 100%);
        background-attachment: fixed;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 140px 0;
      }
      .download-section::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 10%;
        right: 10%;
        width: 400px;
        height: 400px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: pulse 8s infinite ease-in-out;
      }
      .download-section::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 15%;
        left: 5%;
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: pulse 10s infinite ease-in-out reverse;
      }
      @keyframes pulse {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: scale(1);
          opacity: 0.5;
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.2);
          opacity: 0.8;
        }
      }
      .download-background {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 150%;
        height: 200px;
        border-top-left-radius: 50%;
        border-top-right-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #0284c7, #f97316, #ef4444);
        opacity: 0.9;
      }
      .download-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
      }
      .app-screenshot {
        max-width: 450px;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border: 6px solid white;
        transition: transform 0.4s ease;
      }
      .app-screenshot:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05) rotate(-3deg);
      }
      .text-teal {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #0284c7, #3b82f6);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        font-weight: 800;
      }
      .display-4 {
        font-size: 3.2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
      }
      .lead {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #475569;
      }
      .btn-download {
        border-radius: 9999px;
        font-weight: 700;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }
      .btn-download:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      }
      .btn-play-store {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #0ea5e9);
        color: white;
        border: none;
      }
      .btn-play-store:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #0d9488);
      }
      .btn-app-store {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f8fafc);
        color: #1e293b;
        border: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
      }
      .btn-app-store:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc, #e2e8f0);
        border-color: #94a3b8;
      }
      .btn-download img {
        height: 28px;
        width: 28px;
        margin-right: 0.75rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/navbar-landing.ejs') %>
    <section class="download-section">
      <div class="bubble-background">
        <div class="bubble" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background-color: #a7f3d0; top: 10%; left: 10%"></div>
        <div class="bubble" style="width: 96px; height: 96px; background-color: #67e8f9; top: 25%; right: 10%; animation-duration: 12s"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="download-background"></div>
      <div class="container download-content">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-left mb-5 mb-md-0 wow fadeInLeft">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/mobile.png" alt="TBCare App Screenshot" class="img-fluid app-screenshot" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-left wow fadeInRight">
            <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-teal">Dapatkan Aplikasi Kami</h1>
            <p class="lead text-secondary my-4">Uji potensi TBC Anda dengan mudah di mana saja dan kapan saja. Aplikasi TBCare Mobile membantu Anda melakukan pra-skrining dengan teknologi suara batuk yang inovatif.</p>
            <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center justify-content-md-start">
              <a href="#" target="_blank" class="btn btn-download btn-play-store d-inline-flex align-items-center mb-2 mb-md-0 mr-md-3">
                <img src="https://www.gstatic.com/images/branding/product/2x/play_store_48dp.png" alt="Google Play" />
                <span>Download di Google Play</span>
              </a>
              <a href="#" target="_blank" class="btn btn-download btn-app-store d-inline-flex align-items-center">
                <img src="https://www.gstatic.com/images/branding/product/2x/app_store_48dp.png" alt="App Store" />
                <span>Download di App Store</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/footer-landing.ejs') %> <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>
  </body>
</html>
